'''Candi''' chhai [[Yin-nì]] he hìn-yùng yit-chho ló-kú sa̍k-theù ke [[meu-é]], thai-phu-fun chhiùng [[Yin-thu-fu̍t-kau Sṳ̀-thoi]] pûn ngìn kien-li̍p ke.

Chhai yá-phién, sin-thù chhùng-pai [[Fu̍t]] fe̍t-chá [[Yin-thu-kau]] ke [[sṳ̀n-mìn]].

Candi, yá-chak ki-fa m̀-tân-chhiang pâu-hàm meu-é ke yi-sṳ, me voi hìn-yùng phe̍t-chak ló-kú ke Yin-thu-fu̍t-kau Sṳ̀-thoi ke kien-chuk； kiûng-thien (''kraton''), yo̍k-thòng (''petirtaan''), sàng-mùn (''gapura'') tén-tén.

On-cheu Yin-thu-kau ke fap-lî, ''candi'' chhiu-chhiong sṳ̀n-mìn he̍t ke só-chhai, chhiu-he [[Mahameru-sân]]. 

Yin-nì ke candi me-he yit-ke mî-su̍t-phín. Kì ke táng-hong lâu kiâ tî-poi pûn ngìn tiâu-khat.

